{"tid":2110411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Banksy地鐵塗鴉鼓勵戴罩","createTime":"2020-07-16T01:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T02:01:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e12294640638dea6461d791192c1f50c44c4bef","tid":2110411,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T01:58:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200716/2TYS7TAFB3I7MIJ3BD5FTZJTQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200716%2F2TYS7TAFB3I7MIJ3BD5FTZJTQU%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n35IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=73599d98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200716%2F2TYS7TAFB3I7MIJ3BD5FTZJTQU%2F&h=2e9208e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200716/2TYS7TAFB3I7MIJ3BD5FTZJTQU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nBanksy地鐵塗鴉鼓勵戴罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b5MtTcOBrhcXK9aRGGoiQfpOjd8=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AQ4FDY76ML7ZXTKRVDKBI3QPKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb5MtTcOBrhcXK9aRGGoiQfpOjd8%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAQ4FDY76ML7ZXTKRVDKBI3QPKI.jpg&h=7053f289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n駕駛室門外有Banksy名字的塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n英國著名塗鴉藝術家。。。。。。。。。。。鼓勵民眾戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美試疫苗成功 45人有抗體<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扮清潔工叫乘客讓開<br />\n<br />\nBanksy在Instagram上載新。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S_VJfJxxBpc9IAR6ahfJJIscbFk=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B4RP7J53C4LOZVNANCW5HZ67DE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS_VJfJxxBpc9IAR6ahfJJIscbFk%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB4RP7J53C4LOZVNANCW5HZ67DE.jpg&h=2c4b59a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫中沒戴口罩的老鼠打噴嚏。<br />\n<br />\n新作品名為「If You Don't Mask, You Don't Get」，再次出現搗蛋的老鼠，不同的是今次戴上口罩，看起來像在打噴嚏和噴灑消毒箒喱。他又把自己名字塗鴉在駕駛室門上。影片最後拍攝車站月台一幅牆上寫有「I get lockdown」（我被禁足）的字句，正關上的車門則寫上「but I get up again」（但我再次站起來），呼應片中的配樂──英國樂隊Chumbawamba的1997年的歌曲《Tubthumping》的歌詞。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦交通局發聲明指感謝作品「鼓勵公眾戴口罩」，「我們希望讓Banksy在一個合適的地點為乘客創作一個新版本」，但未有回應今次是否與Banksy合作，以及其行為有否構成安全風險，僅指在數天前已根據「禁止塗鴉政策」移除作品。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"d15bae6bb57ca220e64359e856d76d4a47f2ee09","tid":2110411,"uid":94291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"佢啲idea真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}